<bibRefCitation id="42574B35FE44FF8FFCEEF9945806F9C2" author="Knutson, L. V. &amp; Shagudian, E. R. &amp; Sahba, G. H." box="[831,1088,1626,1653]" pageId="4" pageNumber="25" pagination="145 - 155" refId="ref6445" refString="Knutson, L. V., Shagudian, E. R., Sahba, G. H. 1973. Notes on the biology of certain snail-killing flies (Sciomyzidae) from Khuzestan (Iran). Iranian Journal of Public Health, 2 (3), 145 - 155." type="journal article" year="1973">Knutson et al. (1973)</bibRefCitation>
